  06 May 2013; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> gpe-login-0.95-r4.ebuild:
  Automake 1.13 fix

*gpe-login-0.95-r4 (23 Jul 2010)

  23 Jul 2010; Angelo Arrifano <miknix@gentoo.org>
  -gpe-login-0.95-r3.ebuild, +gpe-login-0.95-r4.ebuild,
  +files/gpe-login-min-uid.patch:
  Apply patch to select correct min UID/GID for users. Hardcoded values
  were 100/100 while Gentoo uses 1000/1000. See #312743

  13 Feb 2010; Angelo Arrifano <miknix@gentoo.org> -files/gentoo-badge2.png,
  gpe-login-0.95-r3.ebuild, +files/windowmanager.xsessiond-gentoo:
  Autostart matchbox during user session by default.
  Fetch gentoo badge from mirrors instead of storing it in CVS.

  06 Jul 2009; Angelo Arrifano <miknix@gentoo.org> -gpe-login-0.95.ebuild,
  -gpe-login-0.95-r1.ebuild, -gpe-login-0.95-r2.ebuild:
  Remove deprecated ebuilds.

  06 Jul 2009; Angelo Arrifano <miknix@gentoo.org> +files/gentoo-badge2.png:
  Add file as binary, make cvs happy.

  06 Jul 2009; Angelo Arrifano <miknix@gentoo.org> -files/gentoo-badge2.png:
  Remove file for adding as binary.

*gpe-login-0.95-r3 (04 Jul 2009)

  04 Jul 2009; Angelo Arrifano <miknix@gentoo.org>
  +files/gpe-login-0.95-cleanup.patch, +files/gpe-login.pre-session-gentoo,
